author: @CARAT-ds3hd
text:
English translation
(Intro)
Alright
Yeah-eh-eh-eh-eh-eh
Horanghae
 (Verse 1)
Good morning, hello
It's a nice morning
I roll away the blanket and stand up
Opening the closet, jacket one, two, or three
I think any of them will look good today
 
(Verse 2)
I eat a mouthful of tiger cereal
The milk is white (Yummy, yummy)
I'm overflowing with energy, taking confident steps
I fix my eyes wherever I go, this is my playground
 
(Pre chorus)
Oh yeah, yeah
Today, yeah, yeah
I feel like I'm flying through the sky
I guess it's because I'm wearing animal print
I'm having a good day
 
(Chorus)
Tiger power, yeah, yeah
Tiger power, yeah, yeah
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Sing a song, yeah, a tiger song
Tiger power, yeah, yeah
Tiger power, yeah, yeah
Brown patterns, black patterns
Bring me all the white patterns
Because they all suit me so well
 
(Verse 3)
Don't tease me by calling me a hamster
Because it's really annoying
I'm a tiger so don't do that
I don't know, if you keep doing it behind my back
Then I'll show you what's different about the tiger groove
Take a good look of my moves
There are plenty of things I can do beside roaring
I'm Hoshi, putting the 'ho' in 'horangi'
 (Pre chorus)
Oh yeah, yeah
Today, yeah, yeah
I feel like I'm flying through the sky
I guess it's because I'm wearing animal print
I'm having a good day
 
(Chorus)
Tiger power, yeah, yeah
Tiger power, yeah, yeah
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na-na-na

Tiger power, yeah, yeah
Tiger power, yeah, yeah
